General.Name: BIMobject AB
General.Description: BIMobject AB, a software company, engages in the development of cloud solutions and services within building information modelling (BIM) worldwide. The company offers BIMobject Cloud, a cloud-based marketplace for building and interior design products. It serves architects, construction engineers, and other professionals in the construction industry. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
